nodes.title: Positive Prompt
widgets_values: The beautiful Chinese woman is dressed in traditional Tang dynasty attire, with an elegant and grand style. Her long hair is elegantly styled into a bun, adorned with delicate hair ornaments that add a touch of grace and dignity. Her face is soft and beautiful, with delicate features, gentle eyes, and a subtle smile playing on her lips. Her posture is graceful, her steps light, and her every movement exudes the charm of a classical beauty. The entire look transports one to the flourishing era of the Tang dynasty, evoking a deep sense of traditional culture and beauty.

nodes.title: Positive Prompt
widgets_values:
In this captivating portrait, a young woman with curly hair and striking brown eyes gazes directly into the camera, her expression serious and contemplative. She wears a black and green beret, holding it in place with one hand, while the rest of the fabric falls artfully around her head. The beret, with its intricate design, adds a touch of mystery and intrigue to her appearance.

The background is a warm, earthy brown, providing a stark contrast to her vibrant attire. The lighting is soft and diffused, casting a gentle glow on her face and highlighting the contours of her features. The overall composition of the image creates a sense of depth and dimension, drawing the viewer's eye toward the subject.
